You have to compile spettro from source at present:

Debian/Ubuntu/Mint dependencies:
	apt-get install e17-dev libecore-dev libemotion-dev libsdl-dev
	apt-get install libsndfile-dev	# or libaudiofile-dev - See Makefile
	apt-get install libfftw3-dev libsdl-dev pkg-config
and a compiler of some kind - on Debian/Ubuntu/Mint
	apt-get install build-essential
will do the trick for sure.

	apt-get install git
	git clone git://github.com/martinwguy/spettro
	cd spettro
then
	make
and
	./spettro whatever.wav
